For "The Bird Woman", who feeds the pigeons for years almost every day, on the square outside my window.😍
It is wonderful to see that there are still people who treat these wonderful birds with respect.🖤

node.text:
Finally I can show you the artwork I did for "Tomb Raider Underworld" @tombraider @crystaldynamics 😃🙏
As a biiiig Tomb Raider fan it was so much fun to reinterpret Lara and her evil doppelganger! Thanks so much to the TR team, it was a pleasure to work with you!❤️😍🙏
•••
👉swipe for some making-of pictures!
•••
check out the official @tombraider account to learn more about the project and their 25th aniversary!🖤🎉
•••
#tombraider #tombraiderunderworld #crystaldynamics #laracroft #gameart #digitaldrawing #digitalart #digitalpainting
